item.title: CVE-2019-10390|2024-08-04T22:17:20.412Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20splunk%20plugin
item.description: A sandbox bypass vulnerability in Jenkins Splunk Plugin 1.7.4 and earlier allowed attackers with Overall/Read permission to provide a Groovy script to an HTTP endpoint that can result in arbitrary code execution on the Jenkins master JVM.
